                                        >Principal Officers of the Department of State and Chiefs of
                                        Mission</a> organized by position, country, and name; </li>
                                <li>Details about the <a
                                        href="$app/departmenthistory/travels/secretary">foreign
                                        travels of the Secretaries of State</a> and the <a
                                        href="$app/departmenthistory/travels/president">Presidents
                                        of the United States</a>; and,</li>
                                <li>Lists of the <a href="$app/departmenthistory/visits">visits of
